source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT [FlightPlanId]
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value._value_') as "Value"
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value."@type"') as Type
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value."@unit"') as Unit
,[DataType]
,[AlternateRouteAirportIATACode]
,[WaypointSequenceId]
,[CorrectedValue]
,[CorrectedValueType]
,[CorrectedValueUnit]
,[CorrectedValueSource]
,[TCreatedId]
,[TLoadDate]
,[TFileName]
 FROM [BcAdfLido].[OFP_Waypoint_Tracks_OutboundTrack_Stage] A
 cross apply openjson(Value) b

SELECT [FlightPlanId]
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value._value_') as "Value"
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value."@type"') as Type
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value."@unit"') as Unit
,[DataType]
,[AlternateRouteAirportIATACode]
,[WaypointSequenceId]
,[CorrectedValue]
,[CorrectedValueType]
,[CorrectedValueUnit]
,[CorrectedValueSource]
,[TCreatedId]
,[TLoadDate]
,[TFileName]
 FROM [BcAdfLido].[OFP_Waypoint_Tracks_SegmentTrack_Stage] A
 cross apply openjson(Value) b

SELECT [FlightPlanId]
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value._value_') as "Value"
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value."@type"') as Type
,json_value(b.Value, '$.Value."@unit"') as Unit
,[DataType]
,[AlternateRouteAirportIATACode]
,[WaypointSequenceId]
,[CorrectedValue]
,[CorrectedValueType]
,[CorrectedValueUnit]
,[CorrectedValueSource]
,[TCreatedId]
,[TLoadDate]
,[TFileName]
 FROM [BcAdfLido].[OFP_Waypoint_Tracks_InboundTrack_Stage] A
 cross apply openjson(Value) b

SELECT [FlightPlanId]
,[DataType]
,[AlternateRouteAirportIATACode]
,[WaypointSequenceId]
,b.value as [Function]
,[TCreatedId]
,[TLoadDate]
,[TFileName] 
 FROM [BcAdfLido].[OFP_Waypoint_Function_Stage]
 cross APPLY openjson(
    case when Left([Function],1) ='[' 
     then [Function] 
     else '["'+[Function]+'"]' end ,'$') b
